(Ubuntu 12.04)
=====================
External Requirements
=====================
1. gcc/g++
2. pthreads (libc6)
3. make
4. tcl

command:
#####################
sudo apt-get install gcc g++ libc6 make tcl-dev



==========================
Optional External Packages
==========================
1. tclreadline		GNU Readline Extension for Tcl/Tk
2. libreadline		GNU readline and history libraries [development]
3. tclx			Extended Tcl - shared library
4. tcllib			Standard Tcl Library
5. libdb			Berkeley v4.2 - v4.7  Database Libraries [development]
6. libbluetooth		BlueZ Linux Bluetooth library [development]
7. libgoogle-perftools0	Libraries for CPU and heap analysis
8. libxerces-cs-dev	Validating XML parser library for C++ [development]
9. python			Interactive high-level object-oriented language
10. xsd			XML Data Binding for C++
11. zlib			Compression library [runtime]

command:
#######################
sudo apt-get install tclreadline libreadline-dev tclx8.4 tcllib libdb5.1-dev libbluetooth-dev libgoogle-perftools0 libxerces-c2-dev python xsdcxx zlib1g


**NOTE**
libbluetooth-dev => error saat install dengan libbluetooth, lebih baik di remove jika ketemu error

